			<h3 ><a href="#p1693651">Re: Bidding on Ebay; Ignorance on best Bidding strategy</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=1693651&amp;sid=32f634186e869c535397d6396fbe3059#p1693651"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=200&amp;sid=32f634186e869c535397d6396fbe3059">leonard</a></strong> &raquo; Sun May 12, 2013 4:55 pm </p>

			

