			<div class="content"><blockquote><div><cite>theduke wrote:</cite>I am new to Ebay and Paypal.  I was going to establish a Paypal account.  I registered and entered a credit card, but it also wants my bank checking info in addition to my credit card.  Is that normal?  Why do they need both?</div></blockquote><br />Because PayPal will keep funding from your checking account unless you diligently click the few clicks required to pay via credit card for each and every purchase. They avoid cc fees, you don't get rebates or cc protection.</div>

			

